    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically robust, the VANOS system has been recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. It sits on a factory-tuned suspension with a limited-slip differential providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains tight and the power delivery is linear all the way to the 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-focused machine with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
