    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exceptional power-to-displacement ratio with an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. This example has been properly maintained with documented VANOS bulletproofing and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles high torque loads without fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the powertrain is in peak operational condition, offering the visceral, analog driving experience that defines this generation of M-car.",
